    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but i dont have any breathing issues or anything, i'm pretty healthy. i'm just worried about being too sleepy the next day if i take too much. like, if i just took a tiny bit of melatonin with the zolpidem, would that not be a huge deal? it feels like they'd just complement each other rather than being dangerous.",
